MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2014-0459. State ex rel. Elkins v. Fais.

Franklin App. No. 13AP-870. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County.

*1487Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal, it is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
